CMD:
•	cd.. (Remove Last Path)
•	cd path (Add Path)
•	mkdir folder_name  (Make New Folder)
•	mkdir folder_name1  folder_name2 folder_name3 (Make Multiple Folder)
•	Code . (VS Code Open)

Flutter CMD:
•	flutter create my_app
•	flutter analyze
•	flutter test
•	flutter clean
Flutter Fix:
•	dart fix --dry-run (To preview proposed changes)
•	dart fix --apply (To apply the proposed changes)
Flutter Pub
•	flutter pub get
•	flutter pub outdated
•	flutter pub upgrade
Flutter Web
•	flutter run -d chrome (Run in Chrome using the default renderer option )
•	flutter build web --release (Build your app in release mode, using the default (auto))
•	flutter build web --web-renderer canvaskit --release (Build your app in release mode, using just the Canvas Kit renderer)
•	flutter run -d chrome --web-renderer html --profile (Run your app in profile mode using the HTML renderer)
